_source.text: Actually, I do believe they look 90% better than skyrim, the only problem is the low-poly models, the textures are much higher res and thus don't really need normal maps to look pretty and also there are actually some decent post-processing effects, quoting enbseries developer Boris Vorontsov "Skyrim uses next to no post-processing effects."
